      <title>hexo主题配置备忘录</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/28/hexo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/28/hexo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>修改next主题备忘录</strong>（持续更新）</p><ol><li>修改主题字体。<br>在<code>hexo/themes/next/source/css/_variables/base.styl</code>中修改<code>$font-family-chinese      = &quot;SignPainter&quot;</code>效果图可见我主页<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20190128204515541.jpg?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzMzMzI1OTAx,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>SignPainter 可改成你喜欢的字体。<br>参考：<a href="https://theme-next.iissnan.com/faqs.html#custom-font" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NexT常见问题</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
